PROJECT INFORMATION

Project Name: ChainLines
Repository: <https://github.com/fjungplan/chainlines>
Description: Open-source visualization of professional cycling team history (1900-present)
License: GNU Affero General Public License 3.0
Author: fjungplan
Year: 2025

This is a non-commercial, open-source personal project created for educational
and historical documentation purposes. It is not affiliated with any commercial
entity or professional cycling organization.

