PROJECT DATA LICENSE

1. Compilation: The curated database of cycling team lineages, structural 
   relationships, and historical arrangements contained in this project is 
   licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 
   International (CC-BY-SA 4.0).
   
2. Individual Facts: The individual historical facts (names, dates, results)
   are considered public domain facts. This license applies to the effort of 
   selection, coordination, and arrangement of these facts into the 
   ChainLines lineage model.

3. Third-Party Data: Seed data remains subject to the original terms of the 
   respective sources listed in the "Seed Data Source Acknowledgments" section.

